<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v16" title="Q19_v16" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Considere la expresión <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones es una forma equivalente y simplificada de este producto?</qti-prompt>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El producto dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, esta opción es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, y además <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al multiplicar, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Esta expresión ya está simplificada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El producto correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Esta opción propone <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que no es una forma equivalente del producto.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Esta opción es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Pero el producto dado es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. No se puede transformar <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> en <m:math><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir el producto sin cambiar su significado</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión dada es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math>. El paréntesis indica que 7 multiplica a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Multiplicar los factores numéricos</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión obtenida es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La opción B coincide exactamente con este resultado.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar por qué las otras no corresponden</strong></p>
            <p>Opción A: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Opción C: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> no es igual a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Opción D: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, que tampoco coincide con el producto original simplificado.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La forma equivalente y simplificada de <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>7</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>14</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, la alternativa B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>